{"tid":434422,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"九州六日五夜求評","createTime":"2017-10-13T09:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T15:16:07.000Z","uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd03a5ddc27be18d12fa39b7d6f7c4f28c57649","tid":434422,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"day1 機場搞PASS+BK觀光火車 搭車去博多返酒店放低野 博多車站食野/天神地下街(博多住)<br />\nday2 上晝去太宰府 中午搭車去熊本 坐熊本電車(買熊本市地鐵PASS) 去水前寺成趣園 之後去熊本城+櫻花馬場城彩苑 熊本熊辦公室 (博多住) <br />\nday3 搭由布院之森(觀光火車)去由布院行金鄰湖 湯之坪街道(食野) 搭觀光火車返福岡 去海之中道海濱公園影相 睇水族館+表演 (博多住)<br />\nday4 搭海鷗號(觀光火車)去長崎 和平公園+原爆博物館 眼鏡橋 大浦天主堂 哥拉巴庭園 (長崎住)<br />\nday5 朝早軍艦島 晏晝再玩長崎景點 稻佐山纜車睇黃昏/夜景 (長崎住)<br />\nday6 食野 出機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外未搵食乜好 有冇巴打有好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65635e4632da5902cbe3d288cb4e71e0ae804e57","tid":434422,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dbcdac3f8b646d282e89e35e24841166c44f7c","tid":434422,"uid":5911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"熊本城封咗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e02613f5415f09df7537077defb7d4cf29d75db","tid":434422,"uid":53897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"要注意由布院之森而家行條長路時間耐左好多<br />\n如果仲要即日來回, 可能得返兩三粒鐘觀光, 而搭車就搭左六七粒鐘"},{"pid":"64052cb7d86fc92c2d6809516ea3397c9dce403e","tid":434422,"uid":5911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要注意由布院之森而家行條長路時間耐左好多<br />\n如果仲要即日來回, 可能得返兩三粒鐘觀光, 而搭車就搭左六七粒鐘</blockquote><br />\nDay3應該無咩可能做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 架由布院之森行4粒幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0602f568cd7d1fc2fcf65182ba1b36943565ae","tid":434422,"uid":53897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熊本城封咗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢而家岩架啦<br />\n如果熊本城有開, 佢個行程卜3太趕, 而家剛剛好"},{"pid":"7d300838d40638cc9512479718294988322984d2","tid":434422,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熊本城封咗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢而家岩架啦<br />\n如果熊本城有開, 佢個行程卜3太趕, 而家剛剛好</blockquote><br />\n而家都唔得，熊本城外行一個圈都1個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e377ab9982f26838fae7bf47e98eba458ceb87","tid":434422,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"同埋機場冇得買pass同劃觀光火車指定席<br />\n<br />\n由布院就最多特急去大分轉車，但一定一日行唔晒由布加海之中道"},{"pid":"7af56370016e317228b3bb6c9cfd7e3fbed86d13","tid":434422,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"同埋買5日pass但搭4日車？"},{"pid":"3f32626673d99ba458fac22296978df9244bce45","tid":434422,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋機場冇得買pass同劃觀光火車指定席<br />\n<br />\n由布院就最多特急去大分轉車，但一定一日行唔晒由布加海之中道</blockquote><br />\n我諗住係香港買兌換券 去到換pass同bk觀光火車位<br />\n咁樣可唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efed300ceb27b906537104d0349b618f17b25d9","tid":434422,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋機場冇得買pass同劃觀光火車指定席<br />\n<br />\n由布院就最多特急去大分轉車，但一定一日行唔晒由布加海之中道</blockquote><br />\nklook 買JR PASS 係香港機場換定當地福岡機場換??<br />\n定係香港拎左張JR PASS卡 去當地JR 吸印就用得?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劃觀光火車指定席要去邊度搞?"},{"pid":"00a4ec58fca112958bdd3d01a71dcac2c90bac23","tid":434422,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:16:31.000Z"